{"id":2325,"date":"2021-12-15T17:18:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-15T16:18:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=2325"},"modified":"2022-01-25T23:20:21","modified_gmt":"2022-01-25T22:20:21","slug":"galle-fort","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/galle-fort\/","title":{"rendered":"Galle Fort: Things to do and How to Visit"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Galle Fort<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the 18th century, the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dutch<\/a> built their headquarters, Galle Fort, on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lankan<\/a> coast, taking over from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Portuguese<\/a> rule since the 16th century. They fortified Galle, leaving behind beautiful <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">European<\/a>-style buildings still there today. Later, the British took over the town until Sri Lanka became an independent nation once again.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map.jpg\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka map\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka map\" class=\"wp-image-7429 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1362px) 100vw, 1362px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map.jpg 1362w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-300x423.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-600x846.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-726x1024.jpg 726w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-766x1080.jpg 766w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-1022x1440.jpg 1022w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154303\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-map.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of its extraordinary history, the fort has enormous cultural and architectural value. As such, it&#x2019;s recognized as a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> heritage site to preserve the area&#x2019;s beauty.&#xA0; It was also an important trading port for hundreds of years!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7410\" class=\"wp-image-7410 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylon-postcard-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154338\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-ceylo