t.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2325&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154311\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154311\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-pin-20x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154311\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-pin-398x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Galle Fort: Things to do and How to Visit\" height=\"600\" width=\"398\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"todo\">1. Beautiful Shops at Galle Fort<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best things to do in Galle Fort is simply to walk around the ancient streets, visit the incredible handicraft shops, and admire the old-fashioned <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dutch buildings.<\/a> In fact, Galle Fort has some of the best shops in <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\">Sri Lanka<\/a>! It&#x2019;s the perfect place to buy souvenirs and mementos from your trip.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1.jpg\" alt=\"galle fort sri lanka shop\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"galle fort sri lanka shop\" class=\"wp-image-74593 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-1440x960.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220222\/galle-fort-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Some of our favorite shops in Galle Fort are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Barefoot<\/strong> &#x2013; on the corner of Church and Pedlar Street. This shop is the southern outpost of the stylish Colombo homeware shop.<\/li><li><strong>Orchid House<\/strong> -near the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dutch<\/a> Hospital. This lovely shop sells beautiful handicrafts, sarongs, and gems.<\/li><li><strong>Stick No Bills<\/strong> &#x2013; A fantastic design shop selling fun and colorful graphics printed on postcards and wallpaper.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to also visit the local markets in Galle Fort. Here you&#x2019;ll find tropical fruits, local veggies, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/asia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asian<\/a> spices you can try there and then or take back in your suitcase as a reminder of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>. It&#x2019;s also a fantastic place to see locals going about their day-to-day life in Galle.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping.jpg\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka shopping\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka shopping\" class=\"wp-image-7409 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shopping-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154342\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-shoppin