alle. It&#x2019;s beautiful white facade is impressive, as well as its intricate interior.<\/li><li><strong>Old Dutch Hospital<\/strong> (Hospital Road) &#x2013; one of the oldest buildings in Galle with beautiful white archways that perfectly complement the orange tiled roof.<\/li><li><strong>National Maritime Archaeology Museum<\/strong> (Queens St) &#x2013; an exhibit of ancient marine artifacts removed from shipwrecks off the southern coast of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>All Saints Church<\/strong> (Church St) &#x2013; Anglican style church in a gothic, victorian style.<\/li><\/ol>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house.jpg\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka blue house\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka blue house\" class=\"wp-image-7423 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-1152x1440.jpg 1152w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154314\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-blue-house.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Galle Fort Lighthouse<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Galle Fort Lighthouse is an icon of the town, bordered by palm trees and the deep blue ocean. It&#x2019;s this image that&#x2019;s used for many postcards, brochures, and adverts, luring travelers to the beautiful shores of Sri Lanka.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n\n    <a class=\"ebook-banner ebook-banner--sl\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/shop\/ebooks\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" data-src=\"\/build\/images\/ebooks\/traveling-sri-lanka\/slebook-banner.jpg\" class=\"lazypreload\" height=\"225\" width=\"800\" alt=\"Ebook Sri Lanka\">\n    <\/a>\n    \n\n\n\n<p>&#xA0;This extraordinary building is also the oldest lighthouse in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> (built by the British in 1848), and it&#x2019;s still used today. It&#x2019;s one of the must-sees on your trip to Galle Fort, with the perfect outlook at sunset for some great photos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-photography-tips\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">14 Travel Photography Tips<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse.jpg\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka lighthouse\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka lighthouse\" class=\"wp-image-7413 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-1152x1440.jpg 1152w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154331\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-lighthouse.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. Walk Along Galle Fort Wall<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Galle Fort&#x2019;s wall is where locals and tourists come together and enjoy the beautiful view of the city and the sea. Best of all, you can walk along the perimeter of the fort, gaining various perspectives of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> heritage site and the town.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Start at Galle Fort Lighthouse on the southeastern part of the fort. As you walk towards the northwest side of the Fort, you&#x2019;ll see the Clock Tower which is the connection between Galle City and Galle Fort. The walk around the fort is around a 2km walk with beautiful views over the ocean along the way.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/galle-fort-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hotels in Galle Fort<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/stati