top-2-600x776.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220902\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-rooftop-2-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220902\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-rooftop-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. Sunset on the Fort&#x2019;s Wall<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoying the sunset on the Fort&#x2019;s wall is one of the top things to do in Galle Fort. Both locals and travelers grab a spot alongside the wall with beers and snacks, ready to watch the sun disappear into the sea. Watch the sky explode into color and strike up a conversation with locals nearby.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Look out from Flag Rock Bastion, where you&#x2019;ll see adrenaline seekers jumping from the cliffs. It&#x2019;s heart racing watching them jump from such a height so close to rocks, but the locals are pros, and they put on a great show for onlookers.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Also read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-route-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">U Sri Lanka Travel Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7407 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154347\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-sunset-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo