         <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/mirissa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Things to do in Mirissa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8.jpg\" alt=\"galle fort things to do south coast sri lanka palm swing\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"galle fort things to do south coast sri lanka palm swing\" class=\"wp-image-74627 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25231102\/galle-fort-8.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>7. Watch a Cricket Match&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether it&#x2019;s on the streets, or alongside the fort walls, cricket is a massive part of Galle&#x2019;s way of life. Cricket is synonymous with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> &#x2013; it&#x2019;s their national sport &#x2013; so watching it in the flesh here is an experience. Head to the famous Galle cricket ground, which is a lovely place to enjoy a refreshing drink on a warm summer&#x2019;s day.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to Visit Galle Fort<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Galle Fort has excellent transport links as it&#x2019;s one of the most popular destinations on the south coast. You can take the train from Colombo in roughly 2 hours, directly to the Galle Fort rail station. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are numerous trains every day, and you <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/train-colombo-galle\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">book your train tickets easily online here<\/a> can find a full timetable via the <a href=\"https:\/\/eservices.railway.gov.lk\/schedule\/searchTrain.action?lang=en\">Sri Lankan rail website<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you prefer being more flexible rent a car we recommend renting a car in Sri Lanka through&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>&#xA0;as they work with local car rental companies. When booking through Sunny Cars, all insurances are already included in the price.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220237\/galle-fort-2.jpg\" alt=\"galle fort sri lanka tuk tuk\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"290\" alt=\"galle fort sri lanka tuk tuk\" class=\"wp-image-74595 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220237\/galle-fort-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220237\/galle-fort-2-800x516.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220237\/galle-fort-2-1080x697.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/25220237\/galle-fort-2-450x290.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202