variety of cuisines, but you can find excellent street food close to the fort walls. Some of our favorite places to eat are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol id=\"block-abdc4a82-9ff3-4835-9fa6-895abc552d61\"><li><strong>The Blockhouse<br><\/strong>Delicious and cheap Sri Lankan food with a spectacular roof terrace. <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/blockhouse-galle-fort\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TripAdvisor page<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>Lucky Fort Restaurant<br><\/strong>Go here for Sri Lankan food and some of the best food in Galle! Plus, it&#x2019;s cheap! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g297896-d4766204-Reviews-Lucky_Fort_Restaurant-Galle_Southern_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TripAdvisor page<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>The original Rocket Burger<br><\/strong>Not into Asian food tonight? Go and grab a great burger at Rocket. These burgers were the best we had in Sri Lanka. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g297896-d7158978-Reviews-The_Original_Rocket_Burger-Galle_Southern_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TripAdvisor page<\/a>.<\/li><li><strong>Chambers Restaurant<br><\/strong>This might be a little more expensive, but it&#x2019;s worth it to try all the tasty Turkish and Middle Eastern dishes. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g297896-d8711002-Reviews-Chambers_Restaurant-Galle_Southern_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TripAdvisor page<\/a>.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/galle-dutch-fort-sri-lanka-restaurants.jpg\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka restaurants\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"galle dutch fort sri lanka restaurants\" class=\"wp-image-7415 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920